high_descs: Move left, to directly face the shelves to your left.
Pick up the pen that is next to the bowl on the bottom shelf.
Move right, to be directly facing the bowl.
Put the pen in the bowl.
Pick up the bowl that is holding the pen.
Turn to your right and go to the white table.
Place the bowl on the table in front of the black chair, between the other objects on the table.
anns.task_desc: Place a bowl holding a pen onto a white table.

high_descs: Turn to the left, move towards the door, then turn to the right and face the shelves on the wall.
Pick up the pen on the bottom shelf to the left of the silver bowl.
Turn to the right, move toward the black chair slightly, then turn to the left and face the bottom shelf near the brown boots.
Place the pen in the silver bowl next to the credit card on the bottom shelf.
Pick up the silver bowl containing the pen from the bottom shelf.
Turn to the right and move towards and then face the desk in front of the window.
Place the silver bowl containing the pen on the desk in between the book and the credit card.
anns.task_desc: Place a bowl containing a pen on the desk.

high_descs: Turn left, go straight then turn right at the table
Pick up the pen on the desk
Turn right, then turn left at the table
Place the pen in the dish
Pick up the dish from the table
Turn right, turn left, turn right and straight to the table
Place dish on the desk
anns.task_desc: Get the dish with the pen to the desk
